Marti-geliyaha asalka ah iyo marti-geliyaha dhexdhexaadka ah
Waxaa la ogaaday in labadaba SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV ay ka soo baxeen dufanka waxaana loo gudbiyay aadanaha iyada oo loo marayo bisadaha dufanka iyo geela, siday u kala horreeyaan.
Marka la barbardhigo horumarka SARS-CoV-2 ee kala duwan ee fayrasyada kale ee Corona, duqsiyada ayaa loo tixgeliyey inay yihiin marti-geliyeyaasha asalka ah ee SARS-CoV-2, iyadoo fayraska cusub uu 96% la mid yahay fayrasyada Corona ee u eg SARS ee duqsiyada, waxaana loo yaqaan bat-SL-CoVZX45 iyo bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, marti-geliyaha dhexdhexaadka ah ee fayraska ka caawiyay inuu ka gudbo xannibaadda u dhexeysa kooxaha si uu u dhaco aadanaha ayaa weli aan la garanayn, mana uusan cadeynin habka gudbinta.
J. iyo kuwo kale waxay soo jeediyeen in abeesooyinka ay u gudbiyaan fayraska ka soo baxa duqsiyada, taas oo ay ku lug leedahay dib u habeynta isku midka ah ee ku jirta borotiinka S.
Sida laga soo xigtay daraasad, cilmi baarayaasha ku yaalla Guangzhou, Shiinaha ayaa soo jeediyay in cunnada shimbirta - oo ah naas-nuujinta afka dheer ee shimbirta ah ee inta badan loo isticmaalo daawada dhaqameed ee Shiinaha - ay tahay marti-geliyaha u badan ee SARS-CoV-2 iyadoo lagu saleynayo 99% isku midnimada hidde-wadaag ee fayraska Corona ee laga helay cunnada shimbirta iyo SARS-CoV-2.
