SARS-CoV-2 waxaa lagu sheegay inuu dareemayo ultraviolet iyo heerkulka 56 °C muddo 30 daqiiqo ah; ether, ethanol oo heerka 75% ah, daahirinta ku jirta klor, astaanta peroxyacin, chloroform, iyo xalka dufanka kale, laakiin ma aha chloroxide, si wax ku ool ah ayaa u joojin kara fayraska.
