Jawaabta difaaca jirka ayaa si dhakhso leh ugu biiri doonta dagaalka fayraska.
Unugyada lymphocyte-ka ee T, oo ay ku jiraan unugyada CD4+ iyo CD8+, waxay door muhiim ah ka ciyaaraan difaaca.
CD4+ waxay kicinaysaa unugyada fayraska si ay u soo saaraan unugyo ka hortag ah oo loogu talagalay fayraska, waxayna si toos ah u dilaan unugyada fayraska qaba.
Unugyada caawiya ee T-Cell waxay soo saaraan cytokines-ka caawiya caawiya ee caawiya unugyada difaaca.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, fayraska Corona wuxuu yareyn karaa shaqada unugyada T-ka adoo kicinaya geerida barnaamijka ee unugyada T-ka.
Difaaca jirka ee isku dhafan, oo ay ku jiraan borotiinka isku dhafan sida C3a, C5a iyo antibodies, ayaa sidoo kale lagama maarmaan u ah la dagaalanka cudurka fayraska.
Tusaale ahaan, antibodies ka go'doomada ka soo baxay bukaanka MERS-CoV oo soo kabsaday.
