Febraayo 14, kooxda WHO-da oo ay hogaaminayaan WHO ayaa la diyaariyay Shiinaha si ay u soo bandhigaan khabiiro caalami ah iyo khubarada WHO ee dhulka ku yaal Shiinaha si ay uga caawiyaan maamulka maxalliga ah iyo qiimeynta "dhibcaha daran ee cudurka iyo gudbinta" iyagoo martigelinaya aqoon isweydaarsiyo iyo kulammo hay'ado qaran oo waaweyn, iyo booqashooyin goobo ah si loo qiimeeyo "saameeyaha howlaha jawaabta ee gobollada iyo magaalooyinka, oo ay ku jiraan magaalooyinka iyo meelaha miyiga ah". Febraayo 25, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday in "dunidu ay tahay inay wax badan ka qabato diyaarinta cudurka faafa ee suurtagalka ah", iyadoo tilmaamaysa in ay horay u soo bandhigtay in uu yahay mid caafimaad qaba, laakiin in la xaqiijiyo in uu yahay mid "dhalli ah".
