Enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-de-transformant 2' (ACE2) wuxuu la xiriiraa dusha ka baxsan (cellular membranes) unugyada sanbabada, dareemayaasha, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo sidoo kale mindhicirka.
Angiotensin-default 2 wuxuu ka hortagayaa shaqada angiotensin-default enzyme (ACE) adoo yareynaya qadarka angiotensin-da 2 iyo kordhinaya angiotensin-da (1-7); taas oo ka dhigaysa daawo ballanqaad leh daaweynta cudurrada wadnaha iyo xididdada dhiigga.
Nooca aadanaha ee enzyme waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin 2 waxaa loo yaqaan enzyme methylated oo ka kooban zinc oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada qanjirka iyo unugyada kale.
Proteinka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin 2 transcriptase' wuxuu leeyahay noocyo kala duwan oo ah peptidease M2 oo leh amino terminal, iyo xidhiidhka 'carboxylated chain' oo ah amino acid-ka kelyaha.
Angiotensin 2 enzyme waa borotiinka unidirectional membrane ee nooca 1, oo leh enzymes firfircoon oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Xagga ka baxsan xadka unugyada ee angiotensin 2 waxaa ka soo saara xadka dhexdhexaadka ah ee enzymes-ka loo yaqaan 'shidaz', taas oo keentay in borotiinka dhalaalaya uu ku soo baxo dhiigga oo uu ka soo baxo urin.
Enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-2' waxaa lagu heli karaa xubnaha badankood: wuxuu ku xiran yahay qolofka unugyada unugyada nooca 2 ee sanbabada, unugyada qanjirka hoose, unugyada qanjirka hoose ee dareemayaasha iyo xididdada, iyo sidoo kale unugyada muruqyada laxaadka ee derbiga arterial ee xubnaha badankood.
DNA-ga ee loo yaqaan 'riboxyde' ee loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-2' waxaa lagu heli karaa maskaxda, qaabka maskaxda, meesha hoose ee qanjirka, iyo qanjirka maskaxda.
Waxqabadka ugu muhiimsan ee angiotensin 2 waa inuu u shaqeeyo sida dheelitirka angiotensin 2.
Enzyme-ka beddelaya angiotensin wuxuu kiciyaa hormoonka angiotensin 1 inuu noqdo angiotensin 2 oo xididdada dhiigga ku haya.
Dhanka kale, enzyme-ka beddelaya angiotensin 2 wuxuu ka soo saaraa qaab-dhismeedka karboxylic ee ku jira amino acid-phenol alanine ee angiotensin 2 (aspartite-arginine-valine-thyrocin-isoleucine-hestidine-proline-phenol alanine) wuxuuna u beddelaa angiotensin (1-7), (hestidine-aspartite-arginine-valine-thyrocin-isoleucine-hestidine-proline-phenol alanine).
Enzyme-ka beddelaya angiotensin 2 wuxuu u kala qaybsadaa qaar ka mid ah peptide-yada kale oo ka mid ah [des-arginine9] - bradricenin, aplen, neurotensin, denorphine A, iyo gerelin.
Enzyme-ka beddelaya angiotensin 2 wuxuu sidoo kale xakameynayaa gudbinta qanjirka ee xaddidan ee amino acid-ka SLC6A19, wuxuuna door ka ciyaaraa cudurka Hartnipp.
Enzyme-ka loo beddelay angiotensin 2, oo ah borotiinka loo yaqaan 'transmembrane protein', ayaa ah soo galooyinka ugu waaweyn ee unugyada qaar ka mid ah fayrasyada taajka ah, kuwaas oo ay ka mid yihiin fayraska corona NL63, SARS-CoV (viruska sababa cudurka SARS) iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska keena cudurka COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, borotiinka Spike S1 ee SARS-CoV-2 iyo SARS-CoV-2 waxay la xiriiraan heerka enzymatic ee angiotensin-2 ee ku saabsan dusha unugyada si ay u sameeyaan cellular, waxayna u gudbiyaan viruska iyo enzymka unugyada gudaha ee ku yaal unugyada.
Nidaamkan lagu daro wuxuu u baahan yahay in borotiinka S uu soo saaro enzyme-ka protease-ka ee gudniinka, serine2, oo weli la tijaabiyo daaweyn suurtagal ah. Tani waxay keentaa in qaar ay u maleynayaan in hoos u dhigista heerarka enzymes-ka beddelaya angiotensin 2 ee unugyada ay ka caawin karto ka hortagga cudurka.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, ururo badan oo khabiir ah iyo hay'ado is-xakameynaya ayaa ku talinaya in la sii wado isticmaalka xakameeyayaasha angiotensin-ka ee caadiga ah iyo xannibaadaha aqbalayaasha angiotensin-ka daaweynta.
Daraasad taxane ah iyo falanqayn kale oo lagu sameeyay July 11, 2012 ayaa muujisay in "isticmaalka agitocin-ka-beddelka enzymes-ka-beddelka ay la socdeen 34% hoos u dhac muuqda oo halista cudurka sanbabada marka la barbar dhigo kooxda tixraacda".
Intaa waxaa dheer, "Habaalnimada cudurka sambabada ayaa hoos u dhacday dadka la daaweeyey antibodies-ka angiotensin, kuwaas oo aad u nugul inay qabaan cudurka sambabada, gaar ahaan kuwa qaba garaaca wadnaha ama wadnaha.
Isticmaalka inhibitors-ka angiotensin-ka ayaa hoos u dhigay dhimashada cudurka sambabada, inkastoo natiijooyinka ay ahaayeen kuwo ka yar halista guud ee cudurka sambabada".
Enzyme-ka loo beddelay angiotensin 2 ee bini'aadamka (rhACE2) ayaa la rumeysan yahay inuu noqon doono daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay dhaawacyada sanbabada ee daran, waxaana la ogaaday inuu hagaajinayo dhiigga sanbabada, iyo sidoo kale oksijiin-qaboojinta doofaarka qaba cudurka neefsashada daran ee ay keenaan sonkorta dufanka badan.
Nolosha wareejinta ee angiotensin 2 waxay qiyaastii tahay 10 saacadood, 30 daqiiqo kadibna waxay bilaabataa shaqadeeda, iyadoo shaqadeeda (waqtiga) ay sii socoto ilaa 24 saacadood.
Waxaa jira caddayn badan oo muujinaya in angiotensin 2 oo ka soo jeeda uu noqon karo daaweyn rajo leh dadka qaba xanuunka aan la dulqaadan karin angiotensin 2 ee caadiga ah (RAS) iyo cudurrada la socda heerarka sare ee angiotensin 2 ee dhiigga. Tijaabooyin caafimaad ayaa la qiimeynayaa, saameynta ku yeelashada angiotensin 2 oo ka soo jeeda in lagu daaweeyo cudurka neefsashada daran.
