Inkastoo aan la dhammaystirin tijaabooyin caafimaad, haddana waxaa jira dadaalo badan oo lagu horumarinayo tallaalkaas.
Dhamaadkii Febraayo 2020, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) wuxuu sheegay in uusan filayn in tallaal looga hortago SARS-CoV-2, oo ah fayraska keena, laga heli doono wax ka yar 18 bilood.
Waxaa jiray shan tallaal oo la soo gudbiyay marxaladda koowaad ee daraasadaha ammaanka bishii Abriil.
COVID-19 waxaa la aqoonsaday bishii Diseembar 2019.
2020 waxaa adduunka oo dhan ka dhacay cudur aad u weyn, taas oo keentay maalgashiyo badan iyo cilmi baaris si loo horumariyo tallaal.
Ururo badan ayaa isticmaala genome-yada la daabacay si ay u horumariyaan tallaal laga yaabo in lagu horumariyo SARS-CoV-2.
Shuruudaha ay u baahan tahay dadaalka isbahaysiga ee ku saabsan hal-abuurnimada diyaarinta cudurka faafa ee horumarinta tallaalka, oo la shaaciyay bishii Abriil, waa xawaare, awoodda wax soo saarka, baahinta ballaaran iyo helitaanka caalamiga ah.
Bishii Abriil, aqoonyahannada isbahaysiga ee ku lug leh horumarinta cudurka faafa ayaa sheegay in 10 barnaamij oo farsamo oo kala duwan ay cilmi baarista iyo horumarinta ka socdeen horaantii 2020 si loo abuuro tallaal wax ku ool ah oo ka dhan ah COVID-19.
Hadafka ugu muhiimsan ee barxadda ee loo gudbiyay marxaladda koowaad ee daraasadaha ammaanka waxaa ka mid ah:
DNA (oxygen-ka la'aanta ribose iyo ribose) (horumarinta marxaladda koowaad iyo tallaalka la soo jeediyay: Moderna, iyo mRNA-1273)
Qaadayaasha fayraska (horumariyeha tallaalka marxaladda koowaad iyo tallaalka la soo jeediyay: Moderna, qaadayaasha fayraska qanjirka 'Gland' ee nooca 5)
Sida laga soo xigtay aqoonyahannada isbahaysiga ee ku lug leh horumarinta diyaarinta masiibada bishii Abriil, waxaa jira 115 codsade oo tallaal ah oo marxalado horudhac ah oo horumarineed, 78 mashruuc oo firfircoon ayaa la xaqiijiyay (79, sida laga soo xigtay Machadka Milken), 37 mashruuc oo kale ayaa la shaaciyay, laakiin macluumaad yar ayaa la heli karaa (waxaa la rumeysan yahay inay ku jiraan qorsheynta ama naqshadeynta).
Tijaabada heerka koowaad iyo labaad waxay sameeyaan tijaabooyin caafimaad iyo difaaca, oo badanaa ah kuwo aan kala go 'lahayn, oo si taxadar leh loo xakameeyo, meelo badan, iyadoo la go'aamiyo qiyaaso sax ah oo wax ku ool ah.
Tijaabooyinka marxaladda saddexaad waxay inta badan ku jiraan tiro badan oo ka mid ah ka qaybgalayaasha, oo ay ku jiraan kooxda tixraacda, iyo tijaabinta waxtarka tallaalka ee ka hortagga cudurka, iyadoo la daawado saameynta xun ee qiyaasta ugu fiican.
79 tallaal oo la soo jeediyay oo si firfircoon loo horumarinayo (oo la xaqiijiyay horaantii Abriil 2020), 74 ma aysan weli jirin qiimeyn bini'aadam ah (waxaa wali la raadinayaa "ka hor-cilmiyeed").
Ku dhawaad 24-kii Janaayo 2020 ee Australia, Jaamacadda Queensland ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay baaritaan ku sameyneyso suurtagalnimada in tallaalka molecule-ka ee la isku daro uu ku beddeli karo borotiinka fayraska si uu u kiciyo falcelin difaaca.
Qiyaastii 24-kii Janaayo 2020 ee Kanada, Xarunta Caalamiga ah ee Tallaallada (VIDO-InterVac) ee Jaamacadda Saskatchewan ayaa ku dhawaaqday in la bilaabay shaqada tallaalka, iyadoo ujeedadu tahay in tijaabooyinka aadanaha la bilaabo 2021.
Mashruucyada horumarinta tallaalka ee Xarunta Shiinaha ee Xakamaynta iyo Kahortagga Cudurrada ayaa la shaaciyay Janaayo 26, 2020, iyo Jaamacadda Hong Kong Janaayo 28.
Qiyaastii 29ka Janaayo 2020, shirkadaha farmashiyaha ee Janssen, oo uu hogaaminayo Haneke Schweitmer, ayaa ku dhawaaqay inay bilaabeen inay ka shaqeeyaan horumarinta tallaalka.
Janssen waxay la shaqeyneysaa horumarinta tallaalka afka ah ee ay la leedahay shirkadeeda tikniyoolajiyadda nolosha, Vaxart.
18 Maarso 2020, Emergent BioSolutions waxay ku dhawaaqday wada shaqeyn wax soo saar oo ay la leedahay Vaxart si ay u horumariyaan tallaalka.
Febraayo 8, 2020, shaybaarka OncoGen ee Romania ayaa daabacay daraasad ku saabsan naqshadeynta tallaal leh tikniyoolajiyad la mid ah tan loo isticmaalo daaweynta kansarka tallaalka antibody cusub.
Bishii Maarso 25 madaxa machadka cilmi baarista ayaa ku dhawaaqay in ay soo saareen tallaalka oo ay bilaabeen tijaabooyinka.
Febraayo 27, 2020, shirkadda NuGenerex Immuno-Oncology, oo ah shirkad ka tirsan Generex, ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay bilaabatay mashruuc tallaal ah oo lagu abuuri doono peptide Ii-Key ee COVID-19.
Waxay rabeen inay soo saaraan tallaal lagu tijaabiyo dadka "90 maalmood gudahood".
Bishii Maarso 5, 2020, Jaamacadda Washington ee St. Louis waxay ku dhawaaqday mashaariic ay ku sameysaneyso tallaal.
