Cudurka iyo fayraska waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan 'Corona virus'.
Markii ugu horeysay ee uu ka dhacay Wuhan, Shiinaha, waxaa loo yaqaan fayraska iyo cudurka sida caadiga ah "Coronavirus" iyo "Wuhan Coronavirus".
Bishii Janaayo 2020 ayaa WHO waxay ku talisay in la isticmaalo labada magac ee Coronavirus 2019 iyo cudurka neefsashada ee daran ee la xiriira coronavirus 2019 sida laba magac oo ku meel gaar ah oo loogu talagalay virus iyo cudur sida ku cad tilmaamaha 2015 ee mamnuucaya isticmaalka goobaha magacyada cudurrada iyo fayrasyada.
Labada magac ee rasmiga ah ee COVID-19 iyo SARS-CoV-2 ayaa la sii daayay Febraayo 11, 2020.
Iyada oo awoodaha la xaddidood ee silsiladaha sahayda caadiga ah, shirkadaha warshadaha dhijitaalka ah waxay soo saaraan alaabada daryeelka caafimaadka sida baaritaanka sanka iyo qaybaha neefsashada.
Tusaale ahaan, markii isbitaal Talyaani ah uu si deg deg ah u baahnaa qalab neefsashada, alaab-qeybiyaha ayaa awoodi waayay inuu gaarsiiyo waqtiga loo baahdo, shirkad hooyo oo bilaabay injineernimadeeda ayaa ka hortagtay oo soo saartay 100ka qalab ee loo baahdo hal habeen.
Ka dib markii uu ka dillaacay cudurka COVID-19, aragtiyo shirqool ah iyo macluumaad khaldan iyo khiyaano ah oo ku saabsan asalka cudurka, baaxadda, ka hortagga, daaweynta iyo dhinacyada kale ayaa si dhakhso leh ugu faafiyay internetka.
Dadka ayaa u muuqda inay awoodaan inay viruska u gudbiyaan xayawaanka kale.
Daraasadu waxay ku fashilantay inay hesho caddeyn muujineysa in fayraska uu ku soo kordhay doofaarka, duurka, digaagga.
Ma jiraan daawooyin ama tallaalo lagu ansixiyay daaweynta cudurka.
Hay'adaha dawladda, kooxaha aqooneed iyo cilmi baarayaasha warshadaha ayaa cilmi baaris caalami ah ku sameeya tallaallada iyo daawooyinka COVID-19.
Bishii Maarso, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka wuxuu bilaabay tijaabo "Solidarity Test" si loo qiimeeyo saameynta daaweynta afar ka hortag oo fayras oo jira oo leh waxtarka ugu wanaagsan.
Ma jiro tallaal, laakiin hay'ado kala duwan ayaa si firfircoon u shaqeynaya horumarinta tallaallada la shaandheeyay.
Daraasadaha hore ee SARS-CoV waxaa loo adeegsaday sababtoo ah waxay la mid tahay SARS-CoV-2 iyadoo loo adeegsanayo ACE2 receptors si loo galo unugyada aadanaha.
Saddex istaraatiijiyad oo tallaal ah ayaa la bartay.
Marka hore, cilmi baarayaashu waxay doonayaan inay sameeyaan tallaal buuxa oo ka dhan ah fayraska.
Fayraskan oo kale, ha ahaato mid aan shaqeyn ama dhintay, waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu kiciyo jawaab celinta difaaca degdegga ah ee jirka bini'aadamka ee cudurka COVID-19 ee cusub.
istaraatiijiyada labaad ee tallaalka qaybaha yaryar waxay ujeedkeedu yahay in la sameeyo tallaal ka dhigaya nidaamka difaaca jirka mid u nugul qaybaha yaryar ee fayraska.
Xaaladda SARS-CoV-2, cilmi baaristaani waxay diiradda saareysaa borotiinka SpikeS kaas oo ka caawiya fayraska inuu galo soo-dhoweynta enzyme-ka ACE2.
Istaraatiijiyada saddexaad waxay ku saabsan tahay tallaallada DNA (tallaalada DNA-ga ama RNA-ga, oo ah farsamo cusub oo lagu horumarinayo tallaal).
Tallaabooyinka tijaabada ah ee ka soo baxa mid ka mid ah istaraatiijiyaddan waa in la tijaabiyaa si loo hubiyo in ay yihiin kuwo badbaado leh oo wax ku ool ah. 16-kii Maarso 2020, tijaabada ugu horreysa ee tallaalka ee afar mutadawiciin ah ayaa ka bilaabatay Seattle.
Tallaalka ayaa ku jira hiddo-hore oo aan waxyeello lahayn oo ka soo baxday fayraska cudurka. Kor u qaadista antibody-ka ayaa loo tilmaamay inay tahay caqabad suurtagal ah oo la kulma horumarinta tallaalka SARS-CoV-2, laakiin tani waa mid aan la wadaagin.
Waxaa jira in ka badan 300 tijaabooyin caafimaad oo firfircoon oo socda laga bilaabo Abriil 2020.
Toddoba tijaabo oo daaweyn ah oo la xaqiijiyay oo loogu talagalay malaria ayaa la sameeyay, oo afar daraasadood ay ku jiraan hydroxychloroquine ama chlorine.
Daawooyinka antivirus-ka ee la soo jeediyay in dib loo isticmaalo daaweynta cudurka cusub ayaa ah cilmi baarista ugu badan ee Shiinaha, iyada oo ay ka socoto sagaal tijaabo oo marxaladda saddexaad ah oo ku saabsan Remdesivir oo ka dhex socda dalal badan oo natiijooyinkooda la soo bandhigi doono dhammaadka Abriil.
Dib u eegis firfircoon ayaa lagu sameeyay horumarka bukaanka ee tallaallada COVID-19 iyo dawada laga yaabo inay ka dhacaan April 2020. Waxaa lagu qiimeynayaa dhowr dawada antiviral ee laga heli karo daaweynta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan Remediciver, Chlorokine, Hydroxychloroquine, Lupinavir/Retonavir, Lupinavir/Tonavir oo lagu daro Interferon Beta.
Waxaa jira caddayn hordhac ah oo ku saabsan waxtarka Remdesivir, laga bilaabo Maarso 2020.
Xaaladdayda ayaa hagaagtay bukaannada la daaweeyey Remdesivir ee loo isticmaalo raxmaanka.
Tijaabooyinka heerka saddexaad ee caafimaad ayaa lagu sameeyaa Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chlorokine, oo horey loogu isticmaalay daaweynta malariyada, ayaa lagu sameeyay daraasad Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020, waxayna leedahay natiijooyin bilow ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waxaa jira codsiyo lagu sameeyo dib u eegis la xiriira cilmi baarista.
Maamulka caafimaadka ee Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha waxay kugula talinayaan isticmaalka klorokin.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, Machadka Cilmi-baarista Fayrasyada ee Wuhan wuxuu tilmaamayaa in inkasta oo la kugula talinayo qiyaasta hal garaam, in qiyaastaas la yareeyo ay aad u khatar badan tahay oo ay keeni karto dhimashada.
28 Maarso 2020, Maamulka Cuntada iyo Dawooyinka ayaa ogolaaday isticmaalka degdegga ah ee hydroxychloroquine iyo chlorokine sida ay dhakhaatiirta daaweynta u qiimeeyeen kuwa qaba COVID-19. Daabacaadda 7 ee tilmaamaha Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale ku jira interferon, rephavirin ama omyfenovir si loo isticmaalo daaweynta COVID-19.
Xogta bilowga ah waxay muujineysaa in qiyaaso sare oo ribavirin ah ay lagama maarmaan u yihiin in lagu joojiyo SARS-CoV-2 shaybaarka.
Daraasad dheeraad ah oo ku saabsan saameynta nitasoxaneed ee noolaha ayaa lagu talinayaa in la sameeyo ka dib markii la caddeeyay in la joojiyay heerka hoose ee SARS-CoV-2. Daraasadaha ayaa muujinaya in qaabeynta bilowga ah ee borotiinka Spike ee loo yaqaan 'Termoprophyse Serene Transverse Protease 2' (TMPRS2) ay lagama maarmaan u tahay in SARS-CoV-2 lagu galo iyada oo la falgalayo mustaqbalka ACE2.
Daraasadaha loo sameeyay chlorokine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo la adeegsanayo ama aan la helin azithromycin ayaa ka hortagay in bulshada caafimaadka ay aqbalaan daaweyntaas iyada oo aan la helin daraasad dheeraad ah. Ositamivir ma joojinayo SARS-CoV-2 shaybaarka mana laha door loo yaqaan daaweynta COVID-19.
Duufaanta sitokin-ka waxay noqon kartaa mid ka mid ah waxyaabaha ka dambeeya COVID-19.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in hydroxychloroquine uu leeyahay sifooyinka ka hortagga duufaanka sitokine. Guddiga caafimaadka ee Shiinaha ayaa ku daray Tosilizomab tilmaamaha daaweynta kadib markii la dhammeystiray daraasad yar.
Talyaaniga waxaa lagu sameeyaa tijaabo heer qaran oo aan kala sooc lahayn oo heer heer qaran ah ah, ka dib markii natiijooyin wanaagsan laga helay dadka qaba xaalado aad u xanuunsan.
Marka lagu daro in loo isticmaalo baaritaanka serum ee ferritin si loo ogaado duufaannada cytokine, waxaa loogu talagalay in la hortago horumarka noocan oo kale ah, oo la rumeysan yahay inay sabab u tahay dhimashada dadka qaar ee dhaawacmay.
Maamulka Cuntada iyo Dawooyinka ayaa ansixiyay daaweynta la-hawlgalayaasha 'T-cellular receptor' ee 'anti-chemical' ee 'enterloquin-6 receptor', oo ku saleysan daraasadaha xaaladda soo kabashada ee daaweynta cudurka 'citokine-release syndrome' ee aan ka jawaabin steroid-ka sababo kala duwan sanadkii 2017.
Ilaa hadda, ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo la caddeeyay in tuselizumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay cudurka siducka.
Qaabka loo wareejiyo antibodies-yada la nadiifiyey ee la isku xiray ee ay soo saaraan qalabka difaaca COVID-19 ayaa loo baahan yahay in lagu barto sida hab aan tallaal lahayn oo lagu tallaalo.
istaraatiijiyadani waxay ku tijaabisay SARS natiijadaana waa mid aan la go'aamin karin.
Ka-dejintu waxay ka dhigan tahay habka la filayo ee ay ka shaqeyn karto daaweynta antibody-ka ee ka hortagga SARS-CoV-2.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waxaa laga yaabaa in la isticmaalo farsamooyin kale sida sunta unugyada ku salaysan antibodies, saliid ama labadaba.
Waxaa jira noocyo kale oo daaweyn difaaca antibodies ah, sida isticmaalka antibodies hal-saddex nooc ah, oo la horumarinayo.
Wax soo saarka saliida laysu-daray ee loo yaqaan 'syrupine serum', oo ka kooban qaybta dareeraha ah ee dhiigga bukaanka la bogsaday oo ku jira jirka antibodies gaar ah ee fayraska, ayaa la kordhin karaa si dhakhso leh loo faafiyo.
